    "Details": "Designed by the Marian Hegemony using the most cutting-edge gear available to them, the Ravager is made with the best technology available to the Hegemony. The Marian Hegemony soon began marketing the suit for sale to the open market to help bolster the Hegemony's coffers. The Marians deploy them in squads of five called a contubernium and the suits are designed for that kind of larger deployment. While not particularly well armed, the Ravager has extensive armor coverage, making them extremely durable on the battlefield.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Advanced</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.9</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#2aad3b>Can only mount internal bays, can melee, can not swarm.</b></color>",
